What is a progressive web app or pwa ?

A progressive web app is an installable web app ,what does it mean installable ? it can be installed 
on your system .Still confused !? well it is a web application which should  


Be delivered from a web server (over https) and used just like any normal web application.

Be used offline and have diffrent offline support aspects such as caching resources and dispalying 
offline messages .

Have its own icon on your system home screen once installed .

Provide an app-like experience to users .  

have responsive design (Mobile ,Desktop and tablets) .

Doesn't need app store to be installed .

Technically speaking a pwa should have a web app manifest.json file which has many information about the app such as 

App name,

Icons ,

Splash screen

How to tell browsers about your wpa ?

You simply include a link to a web app manifest file in your app index.html file 

wpas can use service workers for caching resources 

